---
import Analytics from "../components/Analytics.astro";
const pageTitle = "Grazie | GentleTest";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="it">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href={`${base}/images/marchio.png`} />
    <title>{pageTitle}</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@400;600;700&family=Libre+Baskerville:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="thanks">
      <div class="thanks__inner">
        <img
          class="thanks__logo"
          src={`${base}/images/logo-color.png`}
          alt="GentleTest"
          width="200"
          height="142"
        />
        <h1>Grazie, abbiamo ricevuto i tuoi dati.</h1>
        <p>
          Ti richiama una persona del centro nei prossimi momenti, quando
          preferisci, solo per organizzare l'appuntamento. Nessuna vendita al
          telefono.
        </p>
        <p class="thanks__small">A presto, dal centro GentleTest di Palermo.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <style is:global>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Libre Baskerville", Georgia, serif;
        color: #3c1f40;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fde6dc 0%, #fbd2bc 100%);
      }
      .thanks {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1.4rem;
      }
      .thanks__inner {
        max-width: 560px;
      }
      .thanks__logo {
        width: 180px;
        max-width: 55%;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
      .thanks h1 {
        font-family: "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.3rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      .thanks p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .thanks__small {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
    </style>
    <Analytics />
  </body>
</html>
